ADVANCED CERAMIC said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 1.66% to NT$105,458,000 from NT$107,233,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            105,458          107,233    
YOY%              -1.66%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            349,466          357,446    
YOY%              -2.23% 
=================================================================
 